README File

Oshoppe Distro packs common modules and the omega theme used by OpenSourceShoppe in all its projects.

We hope other developers will find this useful and not waste time looking for common modules they need to start developing. 

How to use:
1. run:  drush make --force-complete --prepare-install https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RickBahague/OshoppeDistro/master/oshoppe.make <your_install_dir>

Drush make is required.

Ref: 
https://github.com/makara/buildkit_plus_v7
https://github.com/Wiredcraft/example
https://drupal.org/developing/distributions/drupalorg#drush-make


